des: Some may ask why, I say... I don't know. Introducing the thing you've never really looked for....NONSENSICAL THINGS! Ask it to scramble a sentence or a series of words and you might just get a chuckle out of the ordeal. This skill is not for practicality, just for potential humor or gags.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
